snippet: The United States rowing squad for the London Games was completed after three crews won finals at the Olympic trials in West Windsor, N.J.
abstract: United States 2012 Olympic rowing roster is complete; Ken Jurkowski easily wins the men's single sculls and Sara Hendershot and Sarah Zelenka win the women's pair event.
lead_paragraph: The United States rowing squad for the London Games was completed after three crews won finals at the Olympic trials in West Windsor, N.J.
